---
---

<section class="ai-match" id="ai-matching" aria-labelledby="ai-heading">
  <div class="container" data-reveal="section">
    <div class="ai-match__panel">
      <p class="eyebrow" data-reveal-item>Built-in intelligence</p>
      <h2 id="ai-heading" class="ai-match__title" data-reveal-item>
        AI-powered <span class="gradient-text">deal matching</span>
      </h2>
      <span class="ai-match__line" data-reveal-item aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <p class="ai-match__body" data-reveal-item>
        Every audience and volume profile is different. Our matching intelligence analyzes your trading activity and audience to recommend the exchange and deal structure that maximizes your economics — with data, not guesswork.
      </p>
      <p class="ai-match__note" data-reveal-item>
        Not a trading bot. Not financial advice. Intelligence applied to exchange economics — so you get the right deal, faster.
      </p>
      <span class="ai-match__chip" data-reveal-item>More in the partner portal — coming soon</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ai-match {
    padding-block: 4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .ai-match__panel {
    max-width: 44rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    background:
      linear-gradient(165deg, rgba(228, 198, 90, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%),
      var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .ai-match__title {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .ai-match__line {
    display: block;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 2px;
    margin: 1.25rem auto 0;
    background: var(--gradient-wealth);
  }

  .ai-match__body {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.125rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(244, 244, 250, 0.82);
  }

  .ai-match__note {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .ai-match__chip {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding: 0.4375rem 0.875rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    border: 1px solid rgba(228, 198, 90, 0.2);
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: rgba(228, 198, 90, 0.05);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .ai-match {
      padding-block: 5rem;
    }

    .ai-match__panel {
      padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .ai-match {
      padding-block: 6rem;
    }
  }
</style>
